OL,5, The mother of a boy who died in a "hit 
OL,6, and run" has welcomed a coroner's call 
OL,7, for a manslaughter charge to be        
OL,8, considered against the driver.         
OL,10,FDylan Crossey, 15, died after being hit
OL,11,Fby a BMW driven by David Harwood, 46,  
OL,12,Fof New Longton, in 2016.               
OL,14,FIn 2018, Mr Harwood was cleared of     
OL,15,Fcausing death by dangerous driving due 
OL,16,Fto insufficient evidence.              
OL,18,FCoroner Dr James Adeley halted Dylan's 
OL,19,Finquest and called for a gross         
OL,20,Fnegligence manslaughter investigation. 
